{
  "stem": "5388.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he fixed me up with as an orderly in block six.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Six had about six to nine priests, and then they had a [NON-ENGLISH] who was sick, so I was attending to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, attending, it's really a joke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to put the pot that you eat from, put it under his behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he used to know, he used to put it in, wash it a little bit, and put it together with the other stuff, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what happened was the [NON-ENGLISH] were-- I told you in history, they were claiming that they had a kingdom and Danzig was their headquarters-- in the Middle Ages I'm talking now-- and that the Poles were Polandizing them and the Germans were Germanizing them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he used to buttonhole anybody who wanted to listen, especially if somebody who was before with the League of Nations or somebody, a politician or-- oh.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to buttonhole them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But be that as it may, on Sunday, I used to come to the block where I used to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't sleep there, didn't live there, but I used to come and work there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As an orderly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on Sunday, I used to come and write letters for the [NON-ENGLISH], had to be in German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of them didn't know German, so I used to write a few cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Suddenly, in a camp, you send out mail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who ever heard of it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, you see, for the Jewish prisoner, it was one thing for inmates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Poles and the others, they were-- Danes used to get packages, help the to Jewish boys in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Danes were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
